k Anywhere  Smart phones using  Active Sync  and BlackBerry devices will also be affected  Automated systems that rely on email for notification purposes may experience irregular interruptions in connectivity and may be unable to send email reliably  Cadet email will not be affected and should remain fully available during the maintenance period  During the maintenance window  email access will become intermittent and cannot be guaranteed  End users should plan ahead to minimize the negative impact  Email delivery may be delayed by several hours even after the maintenance is complete  Other systems affected periodically throughout this timeframe will be Angel and Citrix applications  remote vmi edu  If you have any questions  please contact the Help Desk at Help vmi edu or call 7643  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 